## Organizing team ##

The TypeTalks in Brno is organized by [David Březina](http://davi.cz) and some of his students from the [Studio of graphic design](http://www.ffa.vutbr.cz/), Faculty of Fine Arts, University of Technology, Brno. Those students are, namely: Vojtěch Buchta, Kristýna Greplová, Matěj Hanauer, Ondřej Homola, Jiří Chlebus, Anna Marková, Kateřina Soudková.

Thanks to Eben Sorkin and Vít Boček for their proof reading and to [The Brno House of Arts](http://www.dum-umeni.cz/) for their welcoming attitude and affordable price of the great venue.


